        "gg-s5zUHk_e_label": "<p>Read More</p>",
        "ggBp3m2tw1K_text": "<p>This Stuff Determines Cognitive Function</p>",
        "ggGsjfeOLCm_text": "<p>Each time I got worse it felt like my IQ plummeted. Each time I got better it felt like it rocketed up. And I did this numerous times in 10 years.</p>",
