        "checksum": "feff651e1dcd60b0b1688713a2386ead197a8d0001d1357261cbe50cfe4bc2c9_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggEtXyrdZXa_text": "Happy Customers. Real Results",
        "ggZO0qkJ_A2_text": "<p>Over 20,000 people have started their Reviv journey.</p><p>Here are just a few of their stories.</p>",
        "ggBlIrkovF9_text": "<p>Some people even start wondering if something bigger is going on., they haven't seen the real hell which is me 2 weeks ago before starting reviv. Changing structure is the way. I’ve never felt so organized &amp; peace. I've Never felt so organized &amp; peace.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>",
        "gguU6PlALn8_text": "<p>Edward&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggjdTd9hkqo_text": "<p>I feel like most of my brain fog has improved, I don't really understand but it's definitely from reviv. I introduced 3 of my friends in SG.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggshkjcCPAh_text": "<p>Caleb</p>",
        "ggWLvc9lyhv_text": "<p>The differences are just awesome. I feel brighter, like my head is clearer and overall, I feel more like myself again. I feel like I was the kid I was when I was 7–8, just full of energy—honestly, it’s amazing!</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>",
        "gg0HR9Y6wdQ_text": "<p>Hector&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggfhc7DrCik_text": "<p>Just wanted to say thank you for making this mouthguard, I had a exam today and I had to cram until 4am and only slept three hours. I was able to get through the entire day without feeling as tired. Thank you so much for making this mouthguard.</p>",
        "ggI9CmtQUTY_text": "<p>Ben</p>"
      }
